These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, teacher
2 different games are played: domino, billiard
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the teacher is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Job   | teacher    | entrepreneur |
| Game         | billiard | domino    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, frog
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
There 2 different types of food: corn, apple
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Pet      | frog  | snake   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Food     | apple   | corn |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, mauve
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Color         | lilac   | mauve  |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

