.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
2 different pets are kept: bird, snake
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, cain
1. the cain-smoker is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Pet     | snake | bird |
| Cigar   | cain | alhambra    |

 #################################

 
