There 2 different types of food: pineapple, potato
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Pet           | cat     | ferret |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy  |
| Food     | potato      | pineapple |

