.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, roller
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Transport   | van     | roller     |
| Cigar           | chaman          | oliveros     |

